description:
&lt;p&gt;Simply Serve Limited are looking to recruit a PPE Coordinator who will be responsible for management and distribution of PPE (Personal Protective Equipment) throughout the hospital (Yeovil District Hospital NHS Foundation Trust).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will be expected to work weekdays, Monday to Friday 8:30am – 12:30pm.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Key activities include working closely with the Senior Contracts Manager and Inventory Manager, to facilitate the close monitoring of stock levels, storage and onward distribution of all PPE.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder must be enthusiastic, able to communicate effectively across various stakeholders and have a great team ethic.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Polly Hutchinson, Senior Contracts Manager on 01935 383029.&lt;/p&gt;
